name: Tawss Khaa
Lore: 'Female Nimbanel fortune teller. Roams the wastes of Tatooine. Trained in the ways of a Sakiyan hunter. Now tracks them for the Alliance. Risk-taker.',
Text: 'If you just initiated battle where present, predict the winner. If correct, randomly retrieve 1 Force. If incorrect, lose 1 Force. Power +3 when present with opponent''s alien of ability > 3. Immune to attrition < 3.',
